<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=99145427410121></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f99145427410121><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=item.html?item=4532&mid=99145427410121>Who is Velector</a> <a id=fs8 href=item.html?item=4532&mid=99145427410121#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Jun 1st 11:57 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Velector is Sorcerer is the "Boss" mob in Velector's Labrynth.  You used to kill him by sending 80 55+ at him and whack him down to 40%, then rez everybody in and finish him off (he'd be up to 60% or so by the time you were done).  But from what I understand they "fixed" his regen so you can't go after him in waves...so not sure how difficult it is to kill him.  I'm not even sure he's killed very much any more.  Getting this item would be...difficult.<br><br>Blubarby Doll<br>59 Necromancer<br>Terris Thule<br>Clan Ta Veren<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
